{"word":"ἀνακηρύσσω","slug":"ἀνακηρύσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακηρύσσω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to proclaim by voice of herald, publish abroad</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to proclaim as conqueror</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἀνακηρυχθῆναι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to put up to auction</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}